Attributed to David Calderwood or John Murray. End of text dated 1 January 1621. Formerly also STC 5286. Identified as STC 4355a on UMI microfilm reel 1267, and as STC 5286 on UMI microfilm reel 984. Appears at reel 1267 #2 (Bodleian Library copy, identified as STC 4355a), and at reel 984 # 19 (British Library copy, identified as STC 5826.
